weewx-digiwx
Copyright 2024 Matthew Wall
Distributed under terms of the GPLv3

This is a driver for weeWX that collects data from DigiWX hardware.

===============================================================================
Installation

0) install weeWX

1) install this driver

weectl extension install https://github.com/matthewwall/weewx-digiwx/archive/master.zip

2) configure weeWX to use this driver

weectl station reconfigure

3) start weeWX


===============================================================================
Configuration

[DigiWX]
    port = /dev/ttyS0
